{"tid":1221763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班人係咪痴撚線架......","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:20:38.000Z","uid":35854,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"25fcdd2c160ba1335ed75731281d612e21e7d14a","tid":1221763,"uid":35854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:38:28.000Z","msg":"我相信好多後生仔都同我一樣<br />\n一見到D不公不義既人/事都忍唔到手 覺得自己要出聲 甚至行動<br />\n所以先會有咁多人一齊發夢 <br />\n但係一直以黎, 大部份人都係停留係<br />\n&quot;我同你講道理 你唔聽 你係錯 你係仆街&quot; <br />\n或者係見到D反智言論既時候出聲去屌鳩人既層次<br />\n<br />\n但係呢2日 見到咁多人 努力去改變自己 真係去嘗試說服一堆同自己唔同陣營既人<br />\n先係有一班人好撚認真咁去做長輩圖 (唔係暗串對方個種)<br />\n仲有呢個POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1211143/page/6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1211143/page/6</a><br />\n#133個位巴打 真係努力打左一篇長文出黎去說服對方(仲要係成功左)<br />\n仲有好多其他例子不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你地真係好撚勁</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會時刻記住自己有一班咁既戰友 黎緊繼續出黎同大家一齊發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c68384c64a8843077d5f76c0f1c4a9f74890830","tid":1221763,"uid":35854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"推返上黎繼續表揚一眾大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5724f558563ee19b9d77899d2df4e9bd1f83c3a","tid":1221763,"uid":35854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d542699c6e4d22991787b56dfe47273be9e46de","tid":1221763,"uid":122443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:59:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17239223388116e78e973b8785d342e8c48daa72","tid":1221763,"uid":212003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited